title: Click UI - Icon Pack v5.2 APK (Android)
description:
A theme for Nova Launcher, Apex Launcher, Go Launcher Ex, Action Launcher Pro, & some others.
The theme currently contains 410 icons & I'll be constantly updating adding in more. Also includes the 5 wallpapers seen in the screenshots. The icons are HD at 144x144, & look sharp on both phones & tablets.

Go Launcher users! Icon masking isn't supported by Go, so unthemed icons have a circle covering them. You can easily fix this by going into Preferences > Visual settings > under Icons, uncheck 'Show icon base'

Recommended icon sizes:
Nova Launcher (Prime): 110%
Apex Launcher: 110%
Go Launcher: Big
This is NOT a standalone app, you need a launcher such as Go, Apex, Nova, etc that allow custom themes.

Installation:
Install Nova, Apex, or Go launcher (all free in the Play Store)
Install this theme
Find Click UI in any of the launcher's theme settings, then apply.
What's in this version: 
(v5.2)
- New Google Play icons. 
- 15 new icons.
All icon packs are on sale!
Required Android O/S : 2.2+
